{"type": "article", "id": 20621, "title": "爱尔兰设计团队的木椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-13T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071223183WiRrHFxev19TU4P.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t都柏林的设计工作室 notion 和爱尔兰的设计品牌 mourne textiles 合作设计了这把木椅，它曾在米兰设计周和纽约设计周上展示。它的扶手和靠背是一圈间隔很宽的木结构，座位也显得宽阔。对应的木腿是黑色的，很细，与座位在形态和颜色上产生了轻与重的对比。因为独特的造型而令人难忘，可以选择两种织物做靠背，<a href=\"http://www.designbynotion.com/frame/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150506R6POBCioLS0MWmn7.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150507im31XcDCYuvlUjL0.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150508QGASPtrsno1YJuKV.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150509BKiC68IO0Jokpwyq.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"822\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.37\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261505093nCTu9BWwLY2czjq.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"398\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}